TEXT(beginproblem());
BEGIN_TEXT
Problem 43, Section 2.3 page 79.
$BR$BR

For what value of the constants \( a \) and \( b \) is the function \( f \)
continuous for all \( x \)
\[ f( x ) = \begin{cases}
 \dfrac{\sin(a x)}{x}  & \text{ if }  x<0  \quad \quad \\
5 &  \text{ if } x=0 \quad \quad \\
x + b & \text{ if } x>0 \quad \quad
 \end{cases}
\]
$BR $BR \( a = \) \{ans_rule(25) \}
$BR $BR \( b = \) \{ans_rule(25) \}
 





$PAR
END_TEXT

$ans1 =5;
&ANS(std_num_cmp($ans1));
$ans2 = 5;
&ANS(std_num_cmp($ans2));
 
ENDDOCUMENT();